ic guide on hieroglyphics and little me would try making my own. And then when I was a pre-teen I was fucking insane about The Kane Chronicles written by Rick Riordan. Anubis was my favorite, both in the series and as a god in general. I just thought he was super sick. Btw the “blessed n","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ef15dfc7-dcc5-461b-9ba2-6a4d21019ba2_7366735e-2fbc-4830-91b8-09f898e9630e.webp","creator":"Alladeeznuts","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦄 Non-human","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human"],"chats":7395,"messages":165383,"created_at":"2025-02-15T07:35:52.987038+00:00"}